PwC DAT Senior Associate Michael and PwC DAT Associate [insert your name] met with Sam, the Director of the Sage Intacct system, on 6/13/2022 to discuss the user access provisioning procedure over the in-scope system Sage Intacct. New User Access
The target employee's manager/access sponsor raises an IT ticket (Jira system) on an ad hoc basis to commence the user access provisioning process. The ticket also serves as proof of permission. When a ticket is submitted to IT, an automatic email notification is delivered to the system owner (as set in the ticketing system). 
